## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/machorebaseentry">MachORebaseEntry</a> encapsulates the current state in the decompression of rebasing opcodes.

This allows you to iterate through the compressed table of rebasing using: <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error">Error</a> Err = <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error/#a4dfd0813c3d0e0a30439b5a3e9196b59">Error::success()</a>; for (const <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/machorebaseentry">llvm::object::MachORebaseEntry</a> &amp;Entry : Obj-&gt;rebaseTable(&amp;Err)) &#123; &#125; if (Err) &#123; report error ...
